{"tid":2050222,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"劏房波：兩虎相爭 必有一傷 籲美方考慮自身影響 回頭是岸","createTime":"2020-06-04T03:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T06:20:39.000Z","uid":21470,"like":8,"dislike":82,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"9add0f02cd78482920cbc44636106368633991c3","tid":2050222,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:56:45.000Z","msg":"陳茂波籲美國制裁香港前考慮對自身影響<br />\n04.06.2020 11:24<br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波接受央視旗下環球電視網訪問指，指美國在香港利益龐大，多年來賺取貿易順差，希望美方在對港實施制裁前，考慮對美國利益帶來的影響。他表示，本港直接出口對美國的貨值只佔整體出口的0.1%，即使美國取消香港的特殊待遇，對本港經濟影響輕微，但可能會影響投資情緒，因此需要加強對商界解說工作，指不少商界在過去一星期了解定立港區國安法的原因後，感到放鬆，亦同意香港需要港區國安法去回復社會穩定。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波又不同意，港區國安法會侵蝕香港高度自治，反而是協助香港社會穩定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1299171&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1299171%26csid%3D261_341&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY1uXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=03592b61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1299171&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"8eaca7ffd8d769cd2f90252883cbe2ce843b0226","tid":2050222,"uid":605,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":14,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:58:02.000Z","msg":"中國係虎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efcd67425462ceacfe2fb30dc07ee3fba9084ce3","tid":2050222,"uid":118112,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:58:15.000Z","msg":"最傷係佢美國啲物業咋掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23dae43af593d56ee991645128b6f0dc5fbed803","tid":2050222,"uid":72185,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:58:25.000Z","msg":"隻腳斷未?"},{"pid":"5983126f8647024d4b570872b09c96ca6e35839a","tid":2050222,"uid":11067,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkg